{"tid":1114913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［獨居撚］岩岩睇睇下電視發現自己喺到自言自語","createTime":"2019-04-18T19:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T03:45:55.000Z","uid":88491,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd55600815f94d0e53d814a7cf13e59c899649bb","tid":1114913,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:15:38.000Z","msg":"頭先睇緊電視 一邊睇一邊講 ： 哈笑死 / 唔撚係阿？/我屌<br />\n之後突然發現自己喺度自言自語做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗返起前排冬天 ，又會自己係間屋係咁大叫：好撚凍呀救命，仲有起身返工又會一邊吹頭一邊自己講： 屌好眼訓呀好攰 ，口渴想飲水：去倒杯水飲先 ，之後先起身行入廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係連登見慣某幾個會員成日自言自語推po , 發現自己現實生活都開始仲愈黎愈嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都會咁？"},{"pid":"609f6dcf86fcea8054d6dc12b63f8eb6d90c61c9","tid":1114913,"uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"認真 me2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人話過我痴線"},{"pid":"7ee221dff517cd7f6e6ee4864e1640a215a9becc","tid":1114913,"uid":136377,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:17:46.000Z","msg":"有時一個人喺街悶得滯都會自己同自己吹水"},{"pid":"ec867eab757b8b429d3983898ed015b9b71d8af5","tid":1114913,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609f6dcf86fcea8054d6dc12b63f8eb6d90c61c9","tid":1114913,"uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"認真 me2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人話過我痴線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"你係點？<br />\n不過係街外唔會，但一返到屋企就會不自不覺開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7341eb923358b9eeaea4002d3a0b8cd6de91b872","tid":1114913,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec867eab757b8b429d3983898ed015b9b71d8af5","tid":1114913,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609f6dcf86fcea8054d6dc12b63